}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，随着《黑神话：悟空》的持续火爆，游戏中关于蜘蛛精四妹的话题在玩家社区内不断升温。一段被玩家挖掘出的删减对话，更是将四妹这一角色的神秘面纱掀起了一角。 据悉，这段对话最初由一位细心的玩家在贴吧中分享。该玩家表示，这段被删减的对话内容似乎暗示了四妹与游戏中的天命人之间存在着某种不为人知的联系。 这一发现立刻激发了众多玩家的好奇心和探索欲，大家纷纷表示对四妹的故事线充满了期待。有玩家分析认为，四妹的故事线在游戏中呈现出一种留白的状态，这很可能是游戏开发进度问题导致的赶工现象。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666738355"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8rXlnrDWvbsQEAMaCTExMDQ0MTk4MyD2/v62BjAAODNACHIJNjY2NzM4MzU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1726252127.905846", "card_id": "Q_664292534", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么孙悟空明明只学了 7 年本事却基本无敌的存在？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "孙悟空跟随菩提祖师学习明面上只有七年时间，为何正是这七年时间让他基本无敌于天地之间？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664292534"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8rXlnrDWvbsQEAMaCTEwOTg5ODEwNCCErfK1BjAAODRACXIJNjY0MjkyNTM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1726252127.906074", "card_id": "Q_666887905", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么日本动漫的题材能够如此丰富?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "真的挺让我惊讶的，从校园恋爱，日常搞笑，乐队摇滚，露营 / 去南极，到中国动画想都不敢想的什么病娇，黑深残都可以包